descript.abstract: This is the Atlas of Canada Drainage Network Skeleton, Version 6. Some of the flow attributes were missing. These were filled in by hand and are indicated by a "2009" entry under Date_E. The stream arcs were assigned to ocean drainages and the order 3 attribute was fixed using BEACONs Tools.
